OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. Some high cloud is likely at
OL,7,Ftimes though turning the sunshine a
OL,8,Flittle hazy, and the Isles of Scilly
OL,9,Fcould have some cloudier spells.
OL,10,FFeeling rather warm in the light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry across the region
OL,13,Ftonight with plenty of clear spells,
OL,14,Fespecially across central and eastern
OL,15,Fparts. Temperatures will fall under
OL,16,Fthe clear spells to give a patchy
OL,17,Frural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,172,160,301,260,100,100
