OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,7,FMore cloud is expected than on
OL,8,FSaturday, but there will still be
OL,9,Fplenty of bright spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FStaying largely dry at the start of
OL,13,Fnext week with light winds and some
OL,14,Fwarm sunshine. Chilly nights. A
OL,15,Fcooling easterly breeze developing by
OL,16,FWednesday, and perhaps isolated
OL,17,Fshowers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
